@Meddler because I forgot you can't edit titles.

I&#039;m tired of ulting has Shyvana and going right through an enemy, or only carrying them for a short while before going through them regardless. The hitbox is wonky and you never know if you&#039;re actually going to catch someone in it. Shyvana sucks because I can&#039;t just farm to 6 and gank like most farming junglers, because if I rely on my R to gank, I&#039;ll somehow miss someone in the middle of the hitbox and look autistic. 

Tl;Dr Can we make Shyvana&#039;s R hitbox ACTUALLY match the area in which she will carry an enemy?
